{"tid":1535593,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我頭先係個黃衫面前推閘入","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:00:16.000Z","uid":251052,"like":113,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7b869f3f9e6d9be634c4d09f193165be9902aaac","tid":1535593,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><em><ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當我行到閘機前準備跳閘時<br />\n我突然見到個黃衫<br />\n果一刻 我個心離一離<br />\n我只好將手插入褲袋<br />\n攞出銀包拍卡<br />\n<br />\n突然間！我靈機一閃！<br />\n<br />\n我將八達通果面向上 <br />\n果然<br />\n部機感應唔到我張八達通<br />\n而我若無其事地<br />\n用力一推 將支棍推開<br />\n只聽到「噠」一聲<br />\n我便行落月台<br />\n個職員完全冇發現<br />\n但我幾乎感覺到我個心臟就黎跳出黎<br />\n<br />\n呢種刺激感 令我開始上癮"},{"pid":"6312d27872876886b5a179154ecc0c4e173f3003","tid":1535593,"uid":38494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.06 上水 彩園劇場 北區陪著你走音樂x分享會 19:30-22:30</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 黃大仙廣場 螢火之荊集會 16:00-21:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人總結一下九月活動?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534738</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推爆佢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"45ff88f5c8f539fee6cb8132d52056a986d85e04","tid":1535593,"uid":15846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a750708ee09337e926d53a621a748f93d4019edc","tid":1535593,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"使乜扮拍"},{"pid":"6d94516b9127f99fcf5fef3ca74d924c44253da4","tid":1535593,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:15:22.000Z","msg":"跳閘真係會上癮"},{"pid":"51046f0daf308ed19359685efaadbe25a19a1f9f","tid":1535593,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"勁能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e56291a9baed78dcb65bf0e155cddf554ff55c0","tid":1535593,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislik